This hits a lot of my good SCP buttons, particularly the reference to a Foundation Department of Thaumaturgy (Never fails to make me a bit giddy). Solid backstory too, and the object itself gives a cool mental image. The journal entries are a little dramatic and  but that's kind of necessary given the narrative role journal entries play in SCPs, and it fits the theme of the object. The guy making it does sound like a wizard. +1







